The SPARQL query to find the Virginia senators in 2013 is:
```sparql
SELECT DISTINCT ?senator ?senatorLabel WHERE {
  ?senator p:P39 ?positionStatement .
  ?positionStatement ps:P39 wd:Q4416090 . # United States senator
  ?positionStatement pq:P768 ?seat . # electoral district
  VALUES ?seat { wd:Q101498883 wd:Q101498993 } # Virginia Class 1 and Class 2 senate seats
  OPTIONAL { ?positionStatement pq:P580 ?startTime . }
  OPTIONAL { ?positionStatement pq:P582 ?endTime . }
  FILTER (
    (!BOUND(?startTime) || ?startTime <= "2013-12-31T23:59:59Z"^^xsd:dateTime) &&
    (!BOUND(?endTime) || ?endTime >= "2013-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
  )
  OPTIONAL { ?senator rdfs:label ?senatorLabel FILTER (lang(?senatorLabel) = "en") }
}
```
The query results show that the Virginia senators in 2013 were Tim Kaine, Mark Warner, and Jim Webb.

